mily:Arial;\">IRFP</span>）,必须先完成国际财务策划师公会认可的教育课程并通过考试。</span>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"vertical-align:baseline;outline:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;border:0px;color:#2F2F2F;font-family:Arial, Verdana, 宋体;line-height:20px;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"vertical-align:baseline;font-weight:inherit;font-style:inherit;outline:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;border:0px;font-family:宋体;\">现行的<span style=\"vertical-align:baseline;font-weight:inherit;font-style:inherit;outline:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;border:0px;font-family:Arial;\">IRFP</span>教育课程如下：</span>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"vertical-align:baseline;outline:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;border:0px;color:#2F2F2F;font-family:Arial, Verdana, 宋体;line-height:20px;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"vertical-align:baseline;font-weight:inherit;font-style:inherit;outline:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;border:0px;font-family:宋体;\"><span style=\"vertical-align:baseline;font-weight:inherit;font-style:inherit;outline:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;border:0px;font-family:Arial;\">A1</span>&nbsp; 财务策划概论&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 21学时</span>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"vertical-align:baseline;outline:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;border:0px;color:#2F2F2F;font-family:Arial, Verdana, 宋体;line-height:20px;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"vertical-align:baseline;font-weight:inherit;font-style:inherit;outline:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;border:0px;font-family:宋体;\"><span style=\"vertical-align:baseline;font-weight:inherit;font-style:inherit;outline:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;border:0px;font-family:Arial;\">A2</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;投资策划&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 21学时</span>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"vertical-align:baseline;outline:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;border:0px;col