;border:0px;font-family:宋体;\"></span>&nbsp;\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"vertical-align:baseline;outline:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;border:0px;color:#2F2F2F;font-family:Arial, Verdana, 宋体;line-height:20px;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"vertical-align:baseline;font-weight:inherit;font-style:inherit;outline:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;border:0px;font-family:宋体;\">根据<span style=\"vertical-align:baseline;font-weight:inherit;font-style:inherit;outline:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;border:0px;font-family:Arial;\">IARFP</span>要求，注册财务策划师<span style=\"vertical-align:baseline;font-weight:inherit;font-style:inherit;outline:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;border:0px;font-family:Arial;\">IRFP</span>课程专注“公司理财”，课程内容涵盖税务、内控、融资、投资、上市筹划、财务分析、评估、审计等各个方面。公司理财涉及面广，工作量大，技术要求高。因此，<span style=\"vertical-align:baseline;font-weight:inherit;font-style:inherit;outline:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;border:0px;font-family:Arial;\">IARFP</span>要求，每门课程的面授课时不低于21学时。</span>\r\n</div>','','','',48,0,'2014-11-04 15:20:43',0,'本站','管理员','2014-11-04',''),(16,'教育 ','<div align=\"left\" style=\"vertical-align:baseline;outline:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;border:0px;color:#2F2F2F;font-family:Arial, Verdana, 宋体;line-height:20px;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"vertical-align:baseline;font-weight:inherit;font-style:inherit;outline:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;border:0px;font-family:宋体;\">要成为<span style=\"vertical-align:baseline;font-weight:inherit;font-style:inherit;outline:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;border:0px;font-family:Arial;\"> RFP<sup>IA</sup></span> 持证人，申请人必须在任何一间本会认可教学点完成教育课程，掌握财务策划的理论及实务知识。</span> \r\n</div>\r\n<div align=\"left\" style=\"vertical-align:baseline;outline:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;border:0px;color:#2F2F2F;font-family:Arial, Verdana, 宋体;line-height:20px;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n</div>\r\n<div align=\"left\" style=\"vertical-align:baseline;outline:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;border:0px;color:#2F2F2F;font-family:Ar